title: Taylor Henderson - Self Titled Album (2013)
description:
Taylor Henderson

===================================================================================

Taylor Henderson is the self-titled debut studio album by Taylor Henderson, the runner-up of the fifth series of The X Factor Australia, released through Sony Music Australia on 29 November 2013. The album debuted at number one on the ARIA Albums Chart and was certified Platinum by the Australian Recording Industry Association.
